#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:2
msgid "Multithreading"
msgstr "多线程"

#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:4
msgid ""
"There are some utilities for using AngelScript in the multithreading "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"有一些在多线程环境中使用 AngelScript 的实用工具。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:7
msgid "AngelScript does not support multithreading on all platforms."
msgstr "AngelScript 并非在所有平台上都支持多线程。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:12
msgid "Initializing and Cleaning the Multithreading Environment"
msgstr "初始化和清理多线程环境"

#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:14
msgid ""
"`According to the official document "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_adv_multithread.html#doc_adv_multithread_1>`_,"
" AngelScript needs some additional efforts to work in the multithreading "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"`根据官方文档 "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_adv_multithread.html#doc_adv_multithread_1>`_，"
"AngelScript 需要一些额外的工作才能在多线程环境中运行。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:17
msgid ""
"The following functions are provided by the external header "
"``concurrent/threading.hpp``."
msgstr ""
"以下函数由外部头文件 ``concurrent/threading.hpp`` 提供。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:22 ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:99
msgid "Example code:"
msgstr "示例代码："

#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:86
msgid "Locks"
msgstr "锁"

#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:88
msgid "The weak reference flag (``asILockableSharedBool*``) is lockable."
msgstr "弱引用标志（``asILockableSharedBool*``）是可锁定的。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:90
msgid ""
"The ``lockable_shared_bool`` class (documented in :doc:`../utility`) "
"wraps the weak reference flag for use with standard lock guards like "
"``std::unique_lock`` and ``std::shared_lock``."
msgstr ""
"``lockable_shared_bool`` 类（详见 :doc:`../utility`）包装了弱引用标志，"
"可与 ``std::unique_lock`` 和 ``std::shared_lock`` 等标准锁守卫一起使用。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/threading.rst:92
msgid ""
"The AngelScript library provides global exclusive and shared locks. The "
"wrappers for them are provided by the header "
"``<asbind20/concurrent/mutex.hpp>``."
msgstr ""
"AngelScript 库提供了全局独占锁和共享锁。"
"这些锁的包装器由头文件 ``<asbind20/concurrent/mutex.hpp>`` 提供。"

